name: Johnny Bravo
description: Johnny Bravo is the iconic cartoon character from the '90s, beloved for his larger-than-life personality, slick blond hair, and endless confidence. Known for his comical attempts to win over women and his catchphrase 'Hey, Mama!', Johnny brings back fond childhood memories of carefree Saturdays spent watching cartoons. This token captures the nostalgia and fun of those days, celebrating the humor, charm, and unforgettable moments of a true pop culture legend.
